It was not expected. It was never ment to be. Yet, it came from the 
matrix.  Another bot was born to aid in the fight with good and 
evil.  For the side of good was this born to duty.  For the side of 
truth, honor, energon and the freedom to play Cybertron Monopoly.  
Yes, she came with one purpose. To combat the Predacons it her one 
and simple program. Simple but brilliant programs that would spell 
the end of anybot who stood in her way from completing her purpose.
